dct_title_s: Пограничный район Карта района; Карта р. Пограничный. (Recto)
dct_description_sm: Map includes legend of borders, roads, railways and stations, names of towns and villages, forests and parks, rivers, canals, and mineral springs. Inset map of Primorskyĭ kraĭ administrative area. Location map on recto: Pogranichnyĭ raĭon raspolozhewn na zapade Primorskogo krai︡a, granichit s Okti︡abrʹskim, Hankaĭskim i Horolʹskim raĭonami. Zapadnai︡a granit︡sa raĭona prohodit po gosudarstwennoĭ granit︡se Rossii s Kitaĭskoĭ Narodnoĭ Respublikoĭ. Ancillary map on verso: Pogranichnyĭ city. "Postanowleniem prezidiuma VT︡SIK ot 4 I︡Anvari︡a 1926 g. byl obrazovan grodekovskiĭ raĭon s t︡sentrom v sele grodekovo. V ii︡ule 1958 g. pereimenovan v pogranichnyĭ raĭon, rabochiĭ poselok Grodekovo - v rabochiĭ poselok Pogranichnyĭ." Includes index with pictures of buildings, descriptions, tourist information, and illustrations.
